            "title": "Intelligent building installation",
            "summary": "In this renovation project, I designed and implemented a Loxone smart home system. The system architecture was developed in collaboration with a licensed electrician and a certified Loxone installer. Following the design phase, I executed the physical wiring, programming, system commissioning, and troubleshooting. The infrastructure&hellip;",
            "content_html": "\n    <figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\">\n      <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/20240413_164501.jpg\" height=\"1848\" width=\"4000\" alt=\"\"  sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/20240413_164501-xs.jpg 640w ,https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/20240413_164501-sm.jpg 768w ,https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/20240413_164501-md.jpg 1024w ,https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/20240413_164501-lg.jpg 1366w ,https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/20240413_164501-xl.jpg 1600w ,https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/responsive/20240413_164501-2xl.jpg 1920w\">\n      \n    </figure>\n\n  <p>\n    In this renovation project, I designed and implemented a Loxone smart home system. The system architecture was developed in collaboration with a licensed electrician and a certified Loxone installer. Following the design phase, I executed the physical wiring, programming, system commissioning, and troubleshooting.<br><br>The infrastructure is structured in three distribution boards: a main unit serving the ground floor and two sub-distribution boards for the upper and lower levels. The project also features complex automation for a dedicated wellness room.<br><br>Programmed via Loxone Config, the system integrates:<br>\n  </p>\n\n  <ul>\n    <li>Lighting and shading (blinds)</li><li>Underfloor heating and boiler temperature control</li><li>Presence detection and intrusion alarms&nbsp;<br></li><li>Access control (Door locks, Intercom/Doorbell)</li><li>Wellness system controls (pool and sauna)</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <p>\n    The home utilizes several logic modes to automate daily routines, to integrate into a persons life seamlessly:\n  </p>\n\n  <ul>\n    <li>Away Mode: Activates the alarm, closes blinds, turns off lights/motion detection, and lowers the temperature.</li><li>Sleep Mode: Modifies motion detection in bedrooms, dims lights, lowers temperature, closes blinds, and disables audio.</li><li>Lighting Scenes: Adapts internal brightness based on the sun's position and outdoor light intensity.</li><li>Overheating Protection: Automatically adjusts shading to block solar gain and prevent the rooms from overheating.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <div  class=\"gallery-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"gallery\" data-columns=\"1\">\n      <figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20241220_203022.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x1848\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20241220_203022-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"333\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240910_190201.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x1848\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240910_190201-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"333\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20241220_203017.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x1848\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20241220_203017-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"333\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240910_190116.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x1848\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240910_190116-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"333\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20241220_203012.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x1848\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20241220_203012-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"333\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20241225_183411.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x1848\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20241225_183411-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"333\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240722_155938.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x1848\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240722_155938-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"333\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      <figcaption>The upper distribution box, security camera DVR and wifi modem</figcaption>\n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240911_124113.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x1848\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240911_124113-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"333\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      <figcaption>The main distribution box, close to being done</figcaption>\n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240722_164231.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x1848\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://koubakr.github.io/media/posts/3/gallery/20240722_164231-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"333\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
